This program is a repetition-bot in telegram and VKontakte services.

Usage with default parameters: Main
Usage with other parameters  : Main with command line options:

Available options:
-h, --help                                 - Show this help text
-s tel, --service=telegramm                - service Telegramm (default)
-s vc or --service=vkontakte               - service Vcontakte
-r n, --repeat=n n={1..5}                  - number repeat (defaut = 3)
-l v v={d,i,w,e},
--loglevel v v={debug,info,warning,error}  - level logging (defaul = info)

You can choose only one of these services. You can run two instances of
the programm with different services.

Quantity and order of entering command line arguments is unimportant.
The default settings are located in the corresponding files in this
directory (JSON). In these files, you can change only the number of
repetitions, the logging level and the help information output by the Main,
if you change the names bot, tokens or url the program's performance will
be disrupted. If an erroneous input of arguments is made, the program will
use the default values.

Examples usage:
Main
Main --help
Main -s vc --loglevel=error
Main --service=telegramm -r 2 -l d

